name: GuesstheCelebrity
0:
”Alexa, Launch Guess the Celebrity”
”Repeat the Question”
”Give me a hint”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: guess the celebrity
des:
It's a fun quiz on famous celebrities. Alexa asks you 10 questions and you can try to guess the celebrity. You can ask Alexa below options:
 - Help me
 - Give me a hint
 - Repeat the question 
 - Next question
 - What's my score
 - Restart the game
 - Stop the game

At the end of game, Alexa tells you your score.

In the upcoming release, we will make the game multi level where user has to clear the current level to move to the next level. We will also add support for multi player to make it more fun. We will keep on adding more questions to make it more exciting and challenging.

We appreciate your opinion, so please drop us feedback and we will address those as soon as we can.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
